"{\"uid\": \"today.com-news-paris-olympics-maggie-steffens-sister-in-law-lulu-conner-death-rcna164999\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"A Michael Kors Bag, Suede Slippers and More Holiday Gifts at Walmart - Starting at $9    Francesca Gariano  Maggie Steffens is mourning the loss of her sister-in-law, who died two days before the start of the Paris Olympics.\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 224, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2, \"end\": 14, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"score\": 0.9999999403230522, \"rank\": 5.967694837970716e-08, \"text\": \"Michael Kors\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Michael_Kors\"}, {\"begin\": 108, \"end\": 123, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Maggie Steffens\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Maggie_Steffens\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Lulu Conner, the younger sister of Steffens' husband Bobby Conner, died July 24 at the age of 26, Steffens said Aug. 3.\", \"from\": 226, \"to\": 345, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 226, \"end\": 230, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Steffens, captain of the U.S. women's water polo team, posted a tribute to Lulu Conner onInstagramSaturday, sharing three photos that captured the essence of her late sister-in-law.\", \"from\": 347, \"to\": 528, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 422, \"end\": 426, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"tex