ulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The water polo player wrote that the snap was from the \\\"getting ready suite\\\" at her wedding and marked when they were \\\"officially sisters.\\\"\", \"from\": 937, \"to\": 1076, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In the last slide, she shared a snap of the Steffens and Conners families in Paris donning their Team USA gear.\", \"from\": 1077, \"to\": 1188, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1154, \"end\": 1159, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999395186, \"rank\": 6.037679620703632e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"One big family of Steffens & Conners & more living like Lu,\\\" Steffens concluded the caption.\", \"from\": 1190, \"to\": 1283, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1247, \"end\": 1249, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\", \"score\": 0.7835362936806294, \"rank\": 0.21151962337985675, \"text\": \"Lu\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lutetium\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Super support team during this extremely difficult time.\\\"\", \"from\": 1284, \"to\": 1342, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The Associated Pressreported that Lulu Conner died after traveling to Paris to cheer on Steffens and the U.S. women's water polo team on their journey to another gold medal.\", \"from\": 1344, \"to\": 1517, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1378, \"end\": 1382, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}, {\"begin\": 1414, \"end\": 1419, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 0.9999999999395186, \"rank\": 6.037679620703632e-11, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"While it remains unclear how Lulu Conner died, Steffens described her sister-in-law's death as \\\"a medical emergency.\\\"\", \"from\": 1519, \"to\": 1636, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1548, \"end\": 1552, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"She was so excited for the Olympic Games,\\\" Steffens told AP.\", \"from\": 1638, \"to\": 1699, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1696, \"end\": 1698, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999997862687, \"rank\": 1.699762311096725e-10, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"We are really close.\", \"from\": 1700, \"to\": 1721, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She's the light of the world.\", \"from\": 1722, \"to\": 1751, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She just brings so much joy to everyone.\", \"from\": 1752, \"to\": 1792, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"She always brings people together.\\\"\", \"from\": 1793, \"to\": 1828, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"The U.S. women's water polo team defeated Greece on July 27, 15-6.\", \"from\": 1830, \"to\": 1896, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1872, \"end\": 1878, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"score\": 0.9996990114738085, \"rank\": 0.0002687843787352974, \"text\": \"Greece\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Greece\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"During the match, Steffens scored two goals, but told AP \\\"it definitely helps to play\\\" but that she was \\\"so out of body.\\\"\", \"from\": 1897, \"to\": 2018, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1951, \"end\": 1953, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"score\": 0.9999999997862687, \"rank\": 1.699762311096725e-10, \"text\": \"AP\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Associated_Press\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And I just keep trying to remind myself what Lulu would want and how she would be, you know, how can I embody her spirit the best,\\\" Steffens added.\", \"from\": 2020, \"to\": 2168, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2066, \"end\": 2070, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"And Lulu was somebody that she gave 150% to everything she did.\\\"\", \"from\": 2169, \"to\": 2234, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2174, \"end\": 2178, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"score\": 0.9972365421961922, \"rank\": 0.0027710595475425, \"text\": \"Lulu\", \"types\": [\"Q95074\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lulu_Spencer\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The women's water polo teamclinched a spot in the quarterfinals Aug. 2 after defeating France, 17-5.\", \"from\": 2236, \"to\": 2336, \"entities\": [